race.description: All About Glass Batemans Bay Country Maiden Plate
race.comment: EXILED PRINCE (8) was solid on debut when tiring late at Albury before a 4L defeat in a disappointing performance latest. Can improve now third-up and out to the mile for the first time. Happy to overlook last start and expecting him to bounce back in a big way with the gun hoop booked. THE BUS (7) bounced back to form on the quick turnaround, finishing 0.9L off the winner at the Sapphire Coast. Back out to today's track and trip which shouldn't be an issue and Heywood remains in the saddle. Can sit handy and be tough to run down. I DOUBT IT (11) wasn't beaten far last start after settling on the speed over 1300m here last start. Out to the mile now but won't be far away with improvement likely. SACRED INGOT (5) is racing well, missing here two back in a photo before a strong run at Sale latest. Key chance. REVOKE (4) is next best.
